# Internal Go backend origin. The browser only talks to Next (:3000), which
# rewrites /api/* here; SSR fetches target this directly and forward cookies.
BACKEND_INTERNAL_URL=http://localhost:8080

# Public site origin — used for metadata (canonical/OG) and the sitemap.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Google Analytics 4 measurement id. Leave empty to disable analytics entirely.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# Google Ad Manager (GPT). Leave the network code empty to disable ads entirely
# (the in-content slot then shows a placeholder). The ad-unit path served is
# /{NETWORK_CODE}/{AD_UNIT}.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GAM_NETWORK_CODE=123456789
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GAM_AD_UNIT=devnote_in_content

# --- Feature flags (see src/lib/features.ts) ---
# PRO subscription: the /pro page plus every "Upgrade to Pro" entry point
# (account menu, paywall CTA, "remove ads" link). On by default; set to "false"
# to hide it everywhere — the /pro route then 404s.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PRO_ENABLED=false

# --- Donate (PayPal + MoMo) ---
# The donate button/modal appears only when at least one channel below is set,
# and can be force-hidden with NEXT_PUBLIC_DONATE_ENABLED=false.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DONATE_ENABLED=false
# PayPal: renders a "Donate with PayPal" button that opens this link in a new tab.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PAYPAL_DONATE_URL=https://www.paypal.com/paypalme/yourname
# MoMo: the modal shows this QR image (any HTTPS image URL, or a /public path).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_MOMO_QR_URL=https://example.com/momo-qr.png
# MoMo (optional): a deep link / profile URL; adds an extra "Open MoMo" button.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_MOMO_DONATE_URL=https://me.momo.vn/yourname

# --- Cloudflare (OpenNext) deploy notes ---
# `npm run deploy` uses @opennextjs/cloudflare. Two classes of env vars:
#  1) BUILD-TIME (must be set in the shell/CI when running the build):
#     - BACKEND_INTERNAL_URL  → baked into the /api/* rewrite (next.config.ts)
#     - NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID, NEXT_PUBLIC_GAM_* → inlined
#       into the client bundle at build time.
#     - NEXT_PUBLIC_PRO_ENABLED, NEXT_PUBLIC_DONATE_ENABLED,
#       NEXT_PUBLIC_PAYPAL_DONATE_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_MOMO_* → also inlined; set
#       these in the build environment or the flags/links won't take effect.
#  2) RUNTIME (set in wrangler.jsonc `vars` or `wrangler secret put`):
#     - BACKEND_INTERNAL_URL  → read per-request by src/lib/server-api.ts
#   Keep BACKEND_INTERNAL_URL identical in both places. A public HTTPS backend
#   URL is required — Cloudflare Workers cannot reach localhost.
